WEBVTT

01:27.420 --> 01:31.920
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.160 --> 01:34.920
[Episode 16]

02:17.710 --> 02:18.240
Hello?

02:18.870 --> 02:20.730
I found it on the foreign network.

02:21.070 --> 02:23.310
Ms. Yan usually looks gentle and refined.

02:23.310 --> 02:25.840
I didn't expect her
to play so wild in private.

02:25.910 --> 02:26.800
Who is that man?

02:27.280 --> 02:28.470
Do you want to use this video

02:28.470 --> 02:29.630
to humiliate her relentlessly

02:29.630 --> 02:32.190
and make her unable to hold her head up
in front of you for the rest of her life?

02:32.190 --> 02:34.720
Is this low-level method
all you can think of?

02:36.579 --> 02:37.800
Use a safe alt account

02:38.590 --> 02:39.590
to post it.

02:42.530 --> 02:43.850
She is your wife.

02:44.150 --> 02:46.350
Aren't you afraid of a pyrrhic victory?

02:47.860 --> 02:49.329
How could she be my enemy?

02:52.000 --> 02:53.140
An enemy

02:53.360 --> 02:54.350
will defend

02:54.470 --> 02:55.150
and resist.

02:56.000 --> 02:56.750
What we need to do

02:56.750 --> 02:58.680
is not stand against her,

02:59.190 --> 03:00.310
but find a position

03:01.630 --> 03:04.080
where she'll always look up to you.

03:05.520 --> 03:06.710
When she looks up to you

03:06.710 --> 03:07.790
and needs you,

03:07.910 --> 03:10.520
that's how you own the whole relationship.

03:13.400 --> 03:15.330
When she questions your position,

03:15.710 --> 03:17.370
you shouldn't argue with her,

03:18.400 --> 03:20.030
but make her admit

03:22.310 --> 03:24.510
that she can only be in a lower position.

03:25.850 --> 03:28.530
Then she will willingly look up to you.

03:29.520 --> 03:30.400
So is this

03:30.400 --> 03:32.060
how you make her look up to you?

03:37.190 --> 03:38.920
That's all for today's lesson.

03:39.750 --> 03:41.360
I'm afraid you won't be able to digest it
if I say too much.

03:41.360 --> 03:42.360
Wait, wait, wait.

03:42.590 --> 03:43.960
I have one more question.

03:43.960 --> 03:45.520
Why is your tattoo Medusa?

03:46.190 --> 03:48.050
Doesn't everyone who sees Medusa

03:48.360 --> 03:49.310
turn to stone?

03:51.360 --> 03:53.980
But in the end,
her head was cut off by Perseus

03:55.390 --> 03:56.800
and became his medal.

04:23.800 --> 04:24.240
Hello?

04:24.960 --> 04:25.490
Yan Ling.

04:26.480 --> 04:28.210
Have you seen that post online?

04:28.360 --> 04:29.160
What post?

04:29.360 --> 04:31.220
I'll send it for you to take a look.

04:39.670 --> 04:40.150
[Huge plot twist!
I actually saw this on X.]

04:40.170 --> 04:40.570
[A steamy video of the female professor
messing around with her ex-husband.]

04:40.590 --> 04:41.140
[She's this wild
yet accuses others of assault?]

04:42.420 --> 04:43.480
[Maybe intellectuals]

04:43.510 --> 04:45.020
[just have unique ways to relieve stress.]

04:45.580 --> 04:46.230
[How can someone like her be a professor?]
[University professors sure live wild.]

04:52.720 --> 04:58.870
[Police]

05:00.750 --> 05:01.810
I'm sorry, Ms. Yan.

05:02.830 --> 05:03.670
Actually,

05:04.070 --> 05:05.600
when we caught Ouyang
and the others that day,

05:05.600 --> 05:07.720
we confiscated all the videos on the spot

05:07.720 --> 05:08.830
to prevent leakage.

05:08.830 --> 05:10.150
But I guess

05:10.240 --> 05:12.160
when they were playing it,

05:12.180 --> 05:14.510
it had been uploaded
to the foreign network.

05:14.510 --> 05:17.110
And the person
who posted this is very cunning.

05:17.600 --> 05:18.750
In the video he posted,

05:18.750 --> 05:20.510
both of your faces...

05:21.680 --> 05:23.940
and private parts are slightly blurred.

05:24.430 --> 05:25.160
So this behavior

05:25.160 --> 05:26.720
doesn't constitute a crime.

05:26.720 --> 05:28.630
At most, it's civil infringement.

05:28.630 --> 05:29.750
You have to claim

05:29.750 --> 05:30.720
infringement on your reputation

05:30.720 --> 05:32.720
and the right to privacy on your own.

05:33.270 --> 05:33.750
Wait.

05:34.159 --> 05:35.950
Those people are too irresponsible.

05:35.950 --> 05:37.120
That's just nonsense

05:37.120 --> 05:37.920
on there.

05:38.510 --> 05:40.310
Actually, it's really strange.

05:40.510 --> 05:42.950
I've read the records
given by my cybersecurity colleagues.

05:42.950 --> 05:44.190
Many of the accounts in the post

05:44.190 --> 05:45.840
that blindly slander you

05:46.000 --> 05:47.320
were just registered.

05:47.690 --> 05:49.500
They'll use the same content repeatedly

05:49.500 --> 05:51.620
for a while to gain more attention.

05:54.700 --> 05:55.900
What does that mean?

05:57.120 --> 05:57.630
Ms. Yan.

05:58.630 --> 05:59.730
Think carefully,

06:00.240 --> 06:01.240
have you recently

06:01.750 --> 06:02.800
offended anyone?

06:03.360 --> 06:04.820
And I feel like this person

06:05.040 --> 06:06.970
should be quite familiar with you.

06:14.270 --> 06:15.870
I did offend someone.

06:17.720 --> 06:18.950
But he deserved it.

06:19.720 --> 06:21.190
Forget it. Let him be.

06:29.430 --> 06:29.920
Right.

06:31.180 --> 06:33.300
Is it okay when Luo Liang

06:33.830 --> 06:35.159
knows about this video?

06:35.990 --> 06:37.590
I explained it to him before.

06:40.920 --> 06:41.320
Luo...

06:41.830 --> 06:42.630
Who?

06:43.630 --> 06:44.070
I...

06:44.870 --> 06:46.360
I got married a while ago.

06:49.260 --> 06:49.990
Really?

06:50.500 --> 06:52.630
Congratulations, congratulations.

06:52.680 --> 06:53.360
Well, yeah.

06:53.360 --> 06:53.720
Look,

06:53.720 --> 06:55.450
especially at times like this,

06:55.720 --> 06:57.360
your husband should stand behind you

06:57.360 --> 06:59.390
as a solid support,

06:59.830 --> 07:00.120
right?

07:00.120 --> 07:01.870
That's what you call truly reliable.

07:01.870 --> 07:03.720
I'm telling you,
I've seen a lot at the station.

07:03.720 --> 07:05.630
Many couples fight like cats and dogs

07:05.630 --> 07:06.890
over trivial matters.

07:07.240 --> 07:09.040
If your husband has any questions,

07:09.040 --> 07:10.690
tell him to call me.

07:10.920 --> 07:12.900
I'll explain everything clearly to him.

07:12.900 --> 07:14.360
But I have to go on a business trip
these two days.

07:14.360 --> 07:15.130
But it's fine.

07:15.130 --> 07:16.160
I'll have my cybersecurity colleagues

07:16.160 --> 07:17.750
follow up on it.

07:18.750 --> 07:19.190
He...

07:20.160 --> 07:20.950
He won't.

07:21.070 --> 07:21.870
Right, well,

07:21.870 --> 07:23.270
Dr. Luo Liang

07:23.270 --> 07:25.240
is a psychiatrist at Renxin Hospital.

07:25.240 --> 07:26.830
He specializes in helping people

07:26.830 --> 07:27.800
with psychological counseling.

07:27.800 --> 07:29.630
He definitely won't, right?

07:29.630 --> 07:30.430
He won't.

07:32.120 --> 07:38.310
[Sanjie Police Station, Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

07:33.950 --> 07:34.480
If I had known

07:34.480 --> 07:36.510
those jerks would post this video online,

07:36.510 --> 07:38.870
I definitely wouldn't have dragged you
into this mess.

07:38.870 --> 07:40.159
It was my own choice.

07:40.159 --> 07:41.760
It has nothing to do with you.

07:42.560 --> 07:43.750
I've implicated you.

07:43.750 --> 07:45.260
Don't say that.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.240
I'm a guy.

07:46.240 --> 07:48.080
What does it matter what they say?

07:48.080 --> 07:49.040
You're the one being hurt.

07:49.040 --> 07:50.830
You still have to go back
to the university to teach them.

07:50.830 --> 07:51.290
Well...

07:52.920 --> 07:54.040
But I think,

07:54.040 --> 07:54.950
since Officer Li said

07:54.950 --> 07:55.920
that the video has been deleted,

07:55.920 --> 07:57.310
maybe not many people

07:57.310 --> 07:58.190
have seen it.

07:59.120 --> 08:01.610
So don't overthink it.

08:02.070 --> 08:02.800
And then

08:03.160 --> 08:03.650
go back

08:03.870 --> 08:05.750
and explain it clearly to Luo Liang.

08:05.750 --> 08:06.810
So you two won't...

08:08.560 --> 08:10.360
Anyway, Jiale will stay
at my place for now.

08:10.360 --> 08:11.090
Don't worry.

08:13.630 --> 08:15.690
I have a meeting, so I'll leave first.

08:16.440 --> 08:17.700
D-Don't overthink it.

08:18.220 --> 08:18.680
Bye-bye.

08:18.290 --> 08:23.430
[Sanjie Police Station, Qingzhou Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

08:27.950 --> 08:28.490
Lu,

08:28.630 --> 08:30.230
take a look at the data for me.

08:36.630 --> 08:37.360
Lu,

08:37.870 --> 08:39.419
we are middle-aged.

08:39.520 --> 08:41.549
You should take it easy on your kidneys.

08:41.549 --> 08:42.830
You play wild now,

08:43.549 --> 08:45.080
but your body can't take it.

08:48.130 --> 08:48.850
Get lost.

08:49.510 --> 08:50.510
I mean well.

08:52.130 --> 08:53.390
Share with me. Tell me.

08:54.240 --> 08:55.230
What are you doing? We're colleagues!

08:55.230 --> 08:56.070
Lu Yifeng!

08:58.550 --> 08:59.810
You've got some nerve.

09:00.750 --> 09:01.550
Is it funny?

09:05.910 --> 09:07.120
A joke is only funny

09:07.120 --> 09:09.610
if the person involved finds it funny.

09:09.790 --> 09:10.870
I'm telling you,

09:11.020 --> 09:12.630
if Lu wasn't such a nice guy,

09:12.630 --> 09:14.600
he could sue you for sexual harassment!

09:14.600 --> 09:15.270
D-D-Don't.

09:15.270 --> 09:16.120
We're colleagues.

09:16.120 --> 09:17.520
There's no need for this.

09:17.790 --> 09:18.360
Well...

09:18.870 --> 09:20.200
What are you looking at?

09:20.510 --> 09:22.080
Apologize to him right now, Mr. Li.

09:22.080 --> 09:22.780
Well...

09:23.320 --> 09:24.150
Lu,

09:24.600 --> 09:25.580
I'm sorry.

09:28.100 --> 09:30.190
Does this mean you've forgiven me?

09:33.120 --> 09:34.120
What do you think?

09:34.200 --> 09:34.720
Yes.

09:36.000 --> 09:36.540
No.

09:37.030 --> 09:38.240
So, is it a yes or a no?

09:40.270 --> 09:41.960
Do you think I came all the way
to your Meteorological Bureau

09:41.960 --> 09:42.910
to have a big fight with someone

09:42.910 --> 09:44.150
just for fun?

09:45.150 --> 09:46.270
I'm still hungry.

09:46.320 --> 09:47.920
Then I'll take you out to eat.

09:49.510 --> 09:51.790
I know it's not about food.

09:54.080 --> 09:54.870
I know.

09:56.000 --> 09:57.000
It's just that...

09:58.230 --> 10:00.090
No matter what reasons I have now,

10:00.510 --> 10:01.270
no matter how I explain it,

10:01.270 --> 10:02.420
I'm in the wrong.

10:02.790 --> 10:04.670
Because I really acted like a jerk.

10:04.670 --> 10:05.270
I'm sorry.

10:07.880 --> 10:10.360
And I'm not good with words,

10:10.390 --> 10:12.200
and I don't know how to sweet-talk.

10:12.200 --> 10:14.730
Because my sweet words
aren't as sweet as you.

10:15.120 --> 10:16.690
Well, do whatever you want.

10:17.270 --> 10:18.670
Just don't ignore me.

10:19.870 --> 10:20.930
Do whatever I want?

10:25.580 --> 10:28.440
Then you can make it up to me
for the rest of your life.

10:30.870 --> 10:31.960
It's a deal then.

10:33.480 --> 10:35.490
Are you crazy?

10:36.390 --> 10:37.720
I promise. I promise.

10:37.720 --> 10:39.770
I promise to treat you very well.

10:39.870 --> 10:40.640
And...

10:40.670 --> 10:41.730
Alright, alright.

10:43.870 --> 10:45.270
Tomorrow is the weekend.

10:47.120 --> 10:48.960
My parents want to meet you.

10:52.510 --> 10:53.630
So sudden?

10:54.630 --> 10:56.650
I'm not ready yet.

10:57.000 --> 10:58.730
What do our parents like to eat?

10:58.910 --> 11:01.200
Don't worry about
what our parents like to eat now.

11:01.200 --> 11:03.200
I'm starving right now.

11:03.200 --> 11:04.120
Spicy skewer hot pot.

11:04.120 --> 11:04.840
With chicken feet.

11:04.840 --> 11:05.150
Okay.

11:05.150 --> 11:05.810
Two of them.

11:05.870 --> 11:06.390
Two jin.

11:11.200 --> 11:12.670
Your mother's name is He Xiao,

11:12.670 --> 11:13.470
from Diannan.

11:13.670 --> 11:15.800
You lived in Chengyu back then, right?

11:16.440 --> 11:18.540
I contacted your father before,

11:18.720 --> 11:19.880
but he seemed

11:20.000 --> 11:22.160
unwilling to talk about the past.

11:22.480 --> 11:24.200
And he said he was rarely home back then,

11:24.200 --> 11:26.120
so he wasn't very clear on the details.

11:26.120 --> 11:28.320
That's why he gave me your contact info.

11:28.360 --> 11:28.910
Yes.

11:29.320 --> 11:31.120
He was always busy making money,

11:31.440 --> 11:32.900
always on business trips.

11:33.840 --> 11:35.330
So, did you spend

11:35.360 --> 11:38.200
more time with your mother growing up?

11:39.150 --> 11:40.550
You must have had a deep bond,

11:40.550 --> 11:41.010
right?

11:42.460 --> 11:43.550
I was young then.

11:43.870 --> 11:44.870
I don't remember.

11:45.750 --> 11:46.970
But your father said

11:47.390 --> 11:49.470
when your mother divorced him,

11:49.550 --> 11:51.480
she didn't fight for your custody.

11:51.550 --> 11:53.150
-Was it because—
-I told you.

11:53.360 --> 11:54.530
I don't remember.

12:00.080 --> 12:00.660
Ma'am.

12:01.120 --> 12:02.870
-Check out our pool and gym.
-No need.

12:02.870 --> 12:03.840
There's a discount for joining now.

12:03.840 --> 12:05.570
-No, thanks.
-No need. No need.

12:23.750 --> 12:25.210
Since you hate her so much,

12:26.320 --> 12:28.550
do you think she cheated

12:28.550 --> 12:30.880
and abandoned the family, including you?

12:30.910 --> 12:31.840
Stop talking!

12:34.030 --> 12:35.230
I forgot everything.

12:36.550 --> 12:37.550
What if I told you

12:37.550 --> 12:39.690
your mother left you and your father,

12:40.480 --> 12:42.080
and even committed suicide,

12:43.670 --> 12:45.730
because she was deceived by a bad man?

12:52.380 --> 12:53.690
I gave up my family.

12:54.300 --> 12:55.660
I gave up my child, too.

12:56.480 --> 12:59.120
I have nothing but him.

12:59.140 --> 13:02.140
Who was the man
who tricked your mother into cheating?

13:03.000 --> 13:04.400
He was a college student,

13:05.320 --> 13:06.380
also from Diannan.

13:07.150 --> 13:09.420
My mom hired him as my tutor then.

13:10.630 --> 13:11.670
That tutor?

13:12.960 --> 13:13.890
What's his name?

13:19.080 --> 13:19.540
Master.

13:20.150 --> 13:20.610
Master.

13:21.390 --> 13:22.510
I still need to confirm something.

13:22.510 --> 13:22.990
Um,

13:23.550 --> 13:24.720
give me one more day off.

13:24.720 --> 13:25.920
Just one day, please?

13:26.440 --> 13:26.960
Hello?

13:28.010 --> 13:28.870
Hello, Master?

13:29.120 --> 13:29.920
The signal...

13:30.240 --> 13:31.240
The signal is bad.

13:31.550 --> 13:33.120
I can't hear you clearly, Master.

13:33.120 --> 13:34.980
I'll report to you when I get back.

13:36.840 --> 13:37.270
Sir,

13:37.380 --> 13:38.720
go straight
to the high-speed rail station.

13:38.720 --> 13:39.050
Okay.

13:53.960 --> 13:54.440
Hello.

13:54.720 --> 13:55.120
Hello.

13:55.390 --> 13:56.440
Is this Ms. Yan?

13:56.840 --> 13:58.410
I'm a reporter from Today's News.

13:58.410 --> 13:59.080
I'd like to interview you

13:59.080 --> 14:01.150
about what you think of
Ding Zhibo's statement.

14:01.150 --> 14:02.540
I have nothing to say.

14:02.840 --> 14:05.370
He published all the letters
you wrote to him.

14:06.270 --> 14:08.270
It looks like you seduced him first.

14:08.510 --> 14:09.160
Ms. Yan,

14:09.360 --> 14:10.690
how do you explain this?

14:17.120 --> 14:18.050
Writing letters

14:18.270 --> 14:20.470
was the most important emotional bond

14:20.550 --> 14:22.790
between Yan Ling and her beloved father.

14:22.790 --> 14:24.280
After her father died,

14:24.510 --> 14:27.200
she was in pain
and treated me as his substitute,

14:27.440 --> 14:28.900
continuing to write to me.

14:29.000 --> 14:30.910
I couldn't bear to break her heart,

14:30.910 --> 14:32.120
so I didn't refuse.

14:32.470 --> 14:35.200
At first,
they were just a little girl's thoughts.

14:35.200 --> 14:36.270
But gradually,

14:37.000 --> 14:38.460
she grew into a young woman

14:40.030 --> 14:41.840
and mistook this reliance

14:41.910 --> 14:43.090
for love.

14:44.510 --> 14:45.370
These letters

14:46.320 --> 14:47.850
also became a young woman's

14:48.120 --> 14:49.740
passionate, crazy,

14:50.480 --> 14:52.840
and undisguised expressions of love.

14:53.870 --> 14:56.510
She ignited the light of my life,

14:57.670 --> 14:59.000
the fire of my desires,

15:00.440 --> 15:01.700
and the spark of my sin.

15:03.600 --> 15:04.600
I don't blame her.

15:05.870 --> 15:07.120
Even today,

15:08.240 --> 15:09.200
I am still moved

15:09.200 --> 15:11.240
by her overwhelming love back then.

15:12.910 --> 15:14.480
Near the end of my life,

15:15.580 --> 15:16.670
I admit I was wrong.

15:17.840 --> 15:19.100
Because in the end,

15:19.150 --> 15:22.390
I couldn't resist
this beautiful temptation.

15:30.840 --> 15:32.240
It will be fine tomorrow.

15:33.440 --> 15:34.840
It will be fine tomorrow.

15:37.080 --> 15:38.480
It will be fine tomorrow.

15:40.150 --> 15:41.550
Uncle Ding sent a letter.

15:41.970 --> 15:43.570
He wishes us a happy New Year.

15:43.670 --> 15:44.800
You write the reply.

15:45.320 --> 15:47.320
Just a simple greeting is all right.

15:49.120 --> 15:50.050
In my whole life,

15:51.100 --> 15:52.960
I've only written to your father.

15:53.600 --> 15:54.670
I'm a widow now,

15:54.670 --> 15:56.870
so it's not appropriate for me to reply.

15:57.840 --> 15:59.820
But we shouldn't lose our manners.

16:23.910 --> 16:25.040
I'll keep it in mind.

16:29.360 --> 16:30.890
Dear Uncle Ding,

16:31.390 --> 16:34.250
thank you for telling me
those stories about my dad.

16:35.240 --> 16:36.790
It made me feel like I was back

16:36.790 --> 16:38.790
to the days when he took me out to sea.

16:39.480 --> 16:40.980
The little gift you gave me,

16:40.980 --> 16:42.910
along with those books from my dad,

16:43.030 --> 16:46.000
brought me
immense comfort and companionship.

16:46.510 --> 16:47.940
You said the word "Uncle"

16:48.270 --> 16:50.270
made us seem distant and estranged.

16:50.910 --> 16:52.920
You said our mutual understanding

16:52.810 --> 16:54.150
[Mailbox]

16:53.080 --> 16:55.480
had long since transcended age and gender,

16:55.690 --> 16:58.350
making it the most beautiful thing
in the world.

16:59.870 --> 17:02.150
Have you received the letter
I wrote to you?

17:02.150 --> 17:04.050
You asked me to write to you,

17:05.109 --> 17:06.890
but why do you never reply?

17:06.910 --> 17:08.880
School has been open for 2 months now.

17:08.880 --> 17:10.740
I'm not like you little girls,

17:10.920 --> 17:12.319
reserved and shy.

17:14.240 --> 17:15.270
I want to let you

17:15.300 --> 17:17.010
hear my thoughts directly.

17:20.880 --> 17:21.710
Darling,

17:22.109 --> 17:23.030
you said,

17:23.089 --> 17:24.750
"You were born when I was not;

17:24.770 --> 17:26.710
I was born when you were already old."

17:26.710 --> 17:28.770
But love will transcend everything.

17:29.670 --> 17:31.800
I know you love me.

17:31.830 --> 17:34.410
My love will only be more than yours.

17:34.790 --> 17:35.720
Darling,

17:35.830 --> 17:38.170
why do I feel your distance?

17:38.310 --> 17:39.930
It makes me miserable,

17:40.000 --> 17:41.460
and I'm completely stuck.

17:57.400 --> 17:59.660
Sir, smoking is not good for your health.

18:04.000 --> 18:07.480
But it's pretty good
for this wonderful moment.

18:11.110 --> 18:13.070
She obviously wrote to seduce him first,

18:13.070 --> 18:15.110
and now she's pretending to be innocent.

18:15.110 --> 18:15.680
She looks

18:15.680 --> 18:17.350
so sanctimonious,
acting like it's for the kids.

18:17.350 --> 18:18.680
Yan Ling is such a clown.

18:18.750 --> 18:20.680
God knows how slutty she really is.

18:28.070 --> 18:28.670
Hello?

18:29.160 --> 18:30.100
No comment.

18:30.240 --> 18:31.840
We don't accept interviews.

18:34.510 --> 18:35.920
You are making a racket here.

18:35.920 --> 18:37.920
Do you know it affects our students?

18:38.000 --> 18:38.800
Leave, leave!

18:38.820 --> 18:40.280
Go to the security office!

18:50.480 --> 18:51.010
Who is it?

18:51.200 --> 18:52.530
Water meter inspector.

18:55.590 --> 18:56.360
Ms. Yan.

18:56.450 --> 18:57.830
-Do you have anything to respond...
-What are you doing?

18:57.830 --> 18:59.240
To the public letter by Mr. Ding Zhibo?

18:59.240 --> 18:59.790
I've heard many parents...

18:59.790 --> 19:01.350
-Go away!
-Have complained to the school.

19:01.350 --> 19:02.790
They think you are unfit to be a teacher.

19:02.790 --> 19:03.640
Will you resign on your own?

19:03.640 --> 19:04.920
If you keep doing this,
I'll call the police!

19:04.920 --> 19:06.440
-Let go!
-I heard Ding Zhibo

19:06.440 --> 19:07.510
took good care of you and your mother.

19:07.510 --> 19:09.240
He even got you into a key high school.

19:09.240 --> 19:09.840
Is it true?

19:09.960 --> 19:11.030
Ding Zhibo previously gave your school

19:11.030 --> 19:11.400
a 10-million scholarship.

19:11.400 --> 19:12.920
-Go away!
-Did you ask him to donate it

19:12.920 --> 19:14.270
just to keep your job?

19:14.270 --> 19:14.750
Is that true?

19:14.750 --> 19:16.480
-Or do you want to use the past...
-Go away!

19:16.480 --> 19:17.590
To blackmail Mr. Ding?

19:17.590 --> 19:18.110
After failing,

19:18.110 --> 19:19.160
you made a scene at the hospital entrance,

19:19.160 --> 19:20.400
-right?
-Hey, what are you doing?

19:20.400 --> 19:21.110
Stop filming!

19:21.110 --> 19:21.870
Tell me!

19:21.960 --> 19:22.750
What are you doing?

19:22.750 --> 19:23.510
What are you doing?

19:23.510 --> 19:24.910
Who told you to film here?

19:25.720 --> 19:26.580
Stop fighting!

19:26.590 --> 19:27.650
What are you doing?

19:28.880 --> 19:29.510
Stop fighting!

19:29.510 --> 19:30.570
What are you doing?

19:31.550 --> 19:32.610
Give me the camera!

19:32.960 --> 19:35.020
-Don't grab my camera!
-Give it to me!

19:51.590 --> 19:53.160
I didn't expect Dr. Luo to search around,

19:53.160 --> 19:54.550
only to find a woman like her.

19:54.550 --> 19:56.110
You can't blame Dr. Luo.

19:56.310 --> 19:58.200
She's just too good at pretending.

19:58.200 --> 20:00.270
When I saw the video
of her blocking the car at the hospital,

20:00.270 --> 20:01.390
I was so touched.

20:01.680 --> 20:03.680
Who knew she was that kind of person?

20:05.960 --> 20:07.680
No matter what you see on the internet,

20:07.680 --> 20:08.600
it's not true.

20:09.110 --> 20:10.170
Yan Ling is my wife.

20:10.680 --> 20:12.940
I know exactly what kind of person she is.

20:14.700 --> 20:15.760
Let's go. Let's go.

20:19.480 --> 20:20.030
Let's go.

20:24.290 --> 20:25.620
What did the doctor say?

20:27.160 --> 20:28.020
The doctor said

20:28.480 --> 20:29.880
I have a mild concussion.

20:30.180 --> 20:32.510
He told me to go home
and rest for a few days.

20:32.880 --> 20:33.740
Let me take you.

20:36.550 --> 20:38.280
You should go back to our house.

20:38.440 --> 20:39.600
Right now, your address

20:39.600 --> 20:40.920
is definitely known to many reporters.

20:40.390 --> 20:43.700
[In Operation]
[DSA Interventional Treatment Room]

20:41.490 --> 20:43.220
I'm afraid they'll harass you.

20:44.310 --> 20:44.920
It's fine.

20:45.200 --> 20:46.330
I can stay at a hotel.

20:47.560 --> 20:49.890
But maybe right after you enter the hotel,

20:49.920 --> 20:51.850
the reporters will still find you.

20:52.720 --> 20:55.050
At least, few people know you're married.

20:55.960 --> 20:57.960
They probably won't find our house.

20:58.750 --> 20:59.610
These few days,

20:59.830 --> 21:01.960
I can stay in the hospital's on-call room.

21:01.960 --> 21:03.760
It's convenient for check-ups.

21:04.750 --> 21:05.750
Have you seen

21:07.150 --> 21:08.020
those letters?

21:10.310 --> 21:11.160
Yes.

21:15.310 --> 21:18.230
[In Operation]
[DSA Interventional Treatment Room]

21:16.830 --> 21:17.640
But I believe

21:18.550 --> 21:20.510
that was just a trap he set for you

21:20.510 --> 21:21.720
when you were young.

21:24.350 --> 21:26.480
He might have encouraged you to write,

21:26.570 --> 21:28.300
but probably never wrote back.

21:28.960 --> 21:29.620
The letters

21:30.070 --> 21:32.330
satisfied his twisted possessiveness.

21:32.780 --> 21:34.780
They're the so-called proof of love

21:35.480 --> 21:36.720
you left in his hands.

21:38.650 --> 21:40.380
Didn't Attorney Zhou say that?

21:41.160 --> 21:43.890
This is how he takes the opportunity
to smear you.

21:48.000 --> 21:49.660
Is that what you really think?

21:54.990 --> 21:55.800
Of course.

21:57.530 --> 21:59.330
Is there any other possibility?

22:06.750 --> 22:08.960
[Patient Passage]

22:10.100 --> 22:12.290
[Jingxiong, Diannan]

22:27.030 --> 22:27.960
This is the place, right?

22:27.960 --> 22:28.440
Yes, yes.

22:28.440 --> 22:29.400
Thank you, Sir.

22:43.270 --> 22:43.790
Sir,

22:44.310 --> 22:46.400
is there someone named Luo Liang here?

22:46.400 --> 22:47.400
Luo Liang.

22:47.440 --> 22:48.500
Ask over there.

22:51.440 --> 22:51.920
Thanks.

22:58.240 --> 22:59.110
Sirs,

22:59.110 --> 23:01.370
do you have someone named Luo Liang here?

23:03.020 --> 23:04.410
Do you know Luo Liang?

23:07.170 --> 23:08.120
Pass.

23:08.750 --> 23:09.550
Wait a minute.

23:09.680 --> 23:10.920
Bomb. Can you beat it?

23:10.940 --> 23:11.870
Here, I'll bomb.

23:12.240 --> 23:12.920
Wait, wait.

23:12.920 --> 23:13.780
Can you beat it?

23:13.790 --> 23:14.110
Pass.

23:14.110 --> 23:14.550
I'll bomb, and you can't beat it.

23:14.550 --> 23:15.320
Sirs.

23:15.640 --> 23:17.770
Is there someone named Luo Liang here?

23:18.510 --> 23:19.750
Do you know Luo Liang?

23:19.790 --> 23:20.390
Luo Liang.

23:20.560 --> 23:21.480
Your turn to play.

23:21.480 --> 23:21.640
Luo.

23:21.640 --> 23:23.590
Luo, Luo, someone's looking for you.

23:23.590 --> 23:24.240
No, no.

23:24.240 --> 23:25.270
I'm looking for Luo Liang.

23:25.270 --> 23:27.280
I'm asking about Luo Liang's family.

23:27.280 --> 23:28.740
Why are you looking for me?

23:31.110 --> 23:32.200
You are Luo Liang?

23:32.830 --> 23:33.680
100% genuine.

23:33.720 --> 23:34.680
I am Luo Liang.

23:36.110 --> 23:37.000
He is Luo Liang.

23:48.420 --> 23:50.220
Can we just keep the dim light on?

23:52.590 --> 23:54.270
The doctor said it's best
to avoid light for the next few days.

23:54.270 --> 23:55.870
Don't move. Don't look down.

23:55.880 --> 23:56.480
I'll do it.

24:17.270 --> 24:18.170
Are you hungry?

24:19.070 --> 24:21.400
Do you want me
to make you something to eat?

24:23.310 --> 24:25.170
No need. Don't trouble yourself.

24:26.240 --> 24:29.100
With everything that happened
these past few days,

24:29.720 --> 24:31.450
you haven't slept well, right?

24:33.510 --> 24:35.440
I'll leave the room for you to rest.

24:35.720 --> 24:36.400
I'll go outside.

24:36.400 --> 24:36.880
Don't.

24:38.720 --> 24:39.580
Just stay here.

24:48.200 --> 24:48.880
Why?

24:50.640 --> 24:52.110
Why are you so good to me,

24:52.680 --> 24:54.410
but refuse to tell me anything?

24:55.070 --> 24:56.590
I told you everything.

24:57.720 --> 24:58.550
But right now,

24:59.640 --> 25:01.640
I don't even know who you are.

25:10.000 --> 25:11.600
I'm afraid that if I tell you,

25:13.310 --> 25:14.710
you'll leave me for good.

25:23.920 --> 25:24.960
I'm not Luo Liang.

25:33.840 --> 25:34.840
My name is Xiao Su,

25:35.690 --> 25:37.760
born on January 18, 1981

25:37.920 --> 25:39.030
in Diannan.

25:39.900 --> 25:42.160
My dad was an educated youth from Wuzhou.

25:42.480 --> 25:44.410
When he was sent to work in Diannan,

25:44.720 --> 25:45.720
he met my mom.

25:46.480 --> 25:47.880
My mom was a local farmer.

25:48.580 --> 25:49.620
She was pretty

25:50.030 --> 25:50.830
and literate.

25:52.270 --> 25:53.510
She worked in the commune

25:53.510 --> 25:54.480
as a medic.

25:55.680 --> 25:56.940
They met,

25:57.070 --> 25:58.090
got married,

25:58.200 --> 25:59.240
and had my sister.

26:00.350 --> 26:02.010
My sister's name is Xiao Yuan.

26:02.200 --> 26:03.800
She's 12 years older than me.

26:09.400 --> 26:10.460
Also because of us,

26:11.640 --> 26:14.300
my dad never had the chance
to return to the city,

26:14.440 --> 26:15.700
until he broke his legs

26:16.310 --> 26:17.200
while working.

26:17.200 --> 26:17.590
Xiao!

26:17.590 --> 26:18.400
Something happened! Something happened!

26:18.400 --> 26:19.790
Someone broke their legs!

26:19.790 --> 26:20.440
Come here!

26:23.270 --> 26:24.230
Help!

26:24.680 --> 26:25.110
Get a cart!

26:25.110 --> 26:25.990
Someone come!

26:26.640 --> 26:27.480
Help!

26:27.680 --> 26:28.310
Slow down!

26:29.030 --> 26:30.960
Lift him slowly and watch his legs!

26:31.790 --> 26:32.320
Careful!

26:32.350 --> 26:32.880
Careful!

26:33.270 --> 26:34.330
Careful, careful!

26:36.440 --> 26:37.060
Xiao!

26:37.400 --> 26:37.750
Hurry, hurry.

26:37.750 --> 26:38.810
Careful, careful.

26:41.880 --> 26:42.760
Xiao Yuan,

26:42.830 --> 26:44.350
watch your brother!

26:47.350 --> 26:49.010
Later, we returned to Wuzhou.

26:50.290 --> 26:52.890
They were assigned
to a neighborhood factory.

26:53.270 --> 26:55.110
My dad's temper grew worse.

26:55.130 --> 26:56.180
You shameless wretch!

26:56.180 --> 26:57.310
Such a disgrace!

26:57.310 --> 26:58.360
I'll beat you to death!

26:58.360 --> 27:00.440
-Don't stop me, or I'll beat you too!
-Stop!

27:00.440 --> 27:01.590
The three of us

27:02.000 --> 27:03.310
became his punching bags.

27:03.310 --> 27:05.000
Hung out with those punks, huh?

27:05.000 --> 27:06.260
I'll beat you to death!

27:06.600 --> 27:08.330
You're not afraid of pain, huh?

27:11.000 --> 27:11.600
Come here!

27:14.000 --> 27:15.060
-Come back!
-Yuan!

27:15.270 --> 27:15.890
Yuan!

27:17.490 --> 27:19.490
The only bright spot in my childhood

27:19.720 --> 27:20.590
was my sister.

27:24.080 --> 27:25.480
She took beatings for me,

27:26.920 --> 27:28.280
taught me how to sing,

27:29.090 --> 27:30.240
and cut my hair.

27:33.480 --> 27:35.080
She was known for her beauty.

27:36.240 --> 27:37.580
As long as she was there,

27:39.270 --> 27:40.640
no one dared to bully me.

27:42.790 --> 27:43.990
We had a special bond.

27:47.470 --> 27:49.170
We shared the same birthday,

27:51.330 --> 27:53.190
but she's exactly 12 years older.

28:00.480 --> 28:01.110
Yuan.

28:02.720 --> 28:03.310
Yuan.

28:20.160 --> 28:20.660
Here,

28:20.960 --> 28:21.890
pour some for me.

28:34.070 --> 28:34.880
Does it hurt?

28:36.440 --> 28:36.920
No.

28:38.640 --> 28:39.640
My little doctor.

28:50.310 --> 28:50.750
Look,

28:52.160 --> 28:52.890
an airplane.

28:57.880 --> 28:58.680
Study hard.

28:59.870 --> 29:00.870
When I make money,

29:00.970 --> 29:01.920
I'll take you on an airplane,

29:01.920 --> 29:03.650
and we'll live somewhere else.

29:17.110 --> 29:18.040
Unfortunately,

29:19.920 --> 29:21.250
she was tricked by a man.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.340
♪ My love lingers on your face ♪

29:25.630 --> 29:26.770
♪ Flowing freely to every place ♪

29:27.170 --> 29:29.860
♪ The sun rises above the horizon,
shining bright ♪

29:36.680 --> 29:38.110
Jian!

29:38.190 --> 29:39.390
-Jian!
-Jian!

29:39.550 --> 29:40.510
-Jian!
-Jian!

29:40.640 --> 29:41.500
-Jian!
-Jian!

29:41.640 --> 29:42.440
-Jian!
-Jian!

29:58.100 --> 30:00.570
♪ It's like a dream ♪

30:01.420 --> 30:04.350
♪ Our encounter was so fleeting ♪

30:05.600 --> 30:07.050
♪ You came like a spring breeze ♪

30:07.340 --> 30:11.970
♪ Softly blowing into my heart ♪

30:12.900 --> 30:19.600
♪ Where has your smile gone? ♪

30:14.270 --> 30:15.350
When I was 10,

30:17.400 --> 30:18.440
her boyfriend

30:19.650 --> 30:22.220
got her imprisoned for harboring drugs.

30:20.450 --> 30:26.360
♪ That familiar smile I remember so well ♪

30:23.000 --> 30:23.830
Freeze! Police!

30:23.830 --> 30:24.460
Freeze!

30:24.880 --> 30:25.410
Get down!

30:26.720 --> 30:27.190
Freeze!

30:26.790 --> 30:31.500
♪ Do you know that I love you, miss you,
resent you, and long for you? ♪

30:27.350 --> 30:28.900
Why did you take my guitar?

30:31.750 --> 30:34.200
♪ My love will never change ♪

30:35.290 --> 30:38.960
♪ Have you ever thought about ♪

30:35.720 --> 30:36.450
What is this?

30:39.270 --> 30:42.080
♪ The vow we once made? ♪

30:39.330 --> 30:40.190
Take them away!

30:42.770 --> 30:46.470
♪ Even if you're drawn to the daffodils ♪

30:42.890 --> 30:45.620
I heard she went south
after she got out of prison.

30:46.750 --> 30:49.470
♪ Blooming by the water ♪

30:48.480 --> 30:50.610
She's never returned home since then.

30:59.930 --> 31:00.990
You and your sister

31:02.510 --> 31:04.310
both wanted to escape the family

31:05.090 --> 31:06.380
and your father.

31:08.000 --> 31:09.400
So you changed your name

31:10.590 --> 31:12.520
to make a clean break with the past.

31:22.000 --> 31:23.060
It's not just that.

31:28.840 --> 31:30.380
After my sister left home,

31:32.470 --> 31:33.790
my dad took all his resentment

31:33.790 --> 31:35.000
out on me.

31:36.060 --> 31:37.290
I was often beaten.

31:39.820 --> 31:40.950
I hated this family.

31:43.510 --> 31:45.150
So I studied very hard

31:46.400 --> 31:47.830
to escape that place.

31:50.960 --> 31:52.000
Later, I was admitted to

31:52.000 --> 31:54.260
Dongguang Nanshan Medical University.

31:56.510 --> 31:59.370
I really hoped to become
a good doctor in the future.

32:00.640 --> 32:02.050
It was also at that time

32:03.920 --> 32:05.070
that I met a girl.

32:11.270 --> 32:12.530
Her name is Xu Jingyun.

32:15.340 --> 32:15.720
Paw Patrol,

32:15.720 --> 32:16.830
you've found out so quickly.

32:16.830 --> 32:17.870
You're amazing.

32:18.270 --> 32:20.920
You were the one who noticed
something wrong with his identity.

32:20.920 --> 32:23.200
With the help
of the provincial department,

32:23.200 --> 32:25.200
we found out his real name is Xiao Su.

32:25.270 --> 32:26.750
At Dongguang Nanshan Medical University,

32:26.750 --> 32:29.000
he had a criminal record
during his freshman year.

32:29.000 --> 32:30.460
The victim was Xu Jingyun.

32:30.590 --> 32:31.520
Attempted rape.

32:32.520 --> 32:33.490
Rape?

32:53.550 --> 32:55.720
Are you Ms. Xu Jingyun?

33:06.750 --> 33:07.750
At that time,

33:08.270 --> 33:10.030
did he go against your will?

33:22.590 --> 33:23.550
What did Dad say?

33:26.310 --> 33:27.970
Then you should listen to him.

33:29.510 --> 33:30.920
Have Gao come back later

33:30.960 --> 33:31.750
to pick up

33:31.750 --> 33:32.720
your clothes for changing and stuff.

33:32.720 --> 33:33.980
I'll pack them for you.

33:40.490 --> 33:41.420
It's my husband.

33:42.720 --> 33:45.480
He has a meeting at my father's place
early tomorrow morning,

33:45.480 --> 33:46.940
so he won't be coming back.

33:56.720 --> 33:58.250
Actually, most of the time,

33:58.960 --> 34:00.510
I don't even know

34:00.530 --> 34:01.860
what I really want.

34:02.560 --> 34:04.510
I did like him once.

34:04.920 --> 34:05.920
But I also knew

34:06.680 --> 34:07.920
my father would not agree

34:07.920 --> 34:09.780
to me being with someone like him.

34:10.110 --> 34:11.070
Not to mention,

34:12.590 --> 34:14.440
in that kind of way.

34:28.150 --> 34:29.409
Don't worry, Jingyun.

34:30.560 --> 34:32.110
I won't let him off.

34:34.590 --> 34:35.440
So,

34:35.800 --> 34:37.989
until the very end, you never admitted

34:38.150 --> 34:40.550
that you and Xiao Su
were in a relationship?

34:41.480 --> 34:42.070
No.

34:53.469 --> 34:56.090
I was sentenced to 3 years
for attempted rape.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.200
After I got out of prison,

35:01.230 --> 35:03.030
I couldn't continue my studies.

35:06.660 --> 35:07.390
And my hand

35:08.910 --> 35:11.440
made it impossible
for me to become a surgeon.

35:13.160 --> 35:14.890
But she never explained a word.

35:17.890 --> 35:19.430
She never even saw me again.

35:21.430 --> 35:23.490
My father was very angry at that time.

35:25.070 --> 35:27.730
He immediately arranged for me
to study abroad.

35:31.440 --> 35:32.440
Only one thing...

35:34.150 --> 35:34.710
What?

35:39.800 --> 35:41.030
Attempted rape

35:43.030 --> 35:44.490
carries a lighter penalty

35:46.110 --> 35:47.310
than completed rape.

35:48.960 --> 35:49.920
By saying that,

35:51.150 --> 35:53.150
I saved my father from humiliation.

35:54.800 --> 35:56.600
It was also the only small effort

35:57.150 --> 35:59.280
I could make for Xiao Su.

36:01.470 --> 36:02.800
For the first few years,

36:04.440 --> 36:05.370
I was very angry.

36:07.840 --> 36:09.570
I hated her for turning our love

36:10.840 --> 36:12.480
into a crime that was humiliated

36:12.480 --> 36:13.680
and mocked by others.

36:16.540 --> 36:18.390
I hated her for ruining my life.

36:21.710 --> 36:22.740
But later on,

36:24.000 --> 36:25.270
I gradually let it go.

36:28.410 --> 36:30.230
Maybe she just chose to protect herself

36:30.230 --> 36:31.550
in that moment.

36:38.230 --> 36:39.230
She's not like me.

36:40.150 --> 36:41.320
I have no one to depend on,

36:41.320 --> 36:42.720
and no one cares about me.

36:45.230 --> 36:46.890
I believe she had her reasons.

36:49.190 --> 36:50.070
Since then,

36:52.760 --> 36:54.560
my life has completely changed.

36:56.400 --> 36:58.000
I didn't dare to tell anyone,

36:59.440 --> 37:01.700
and I just sneaked back to Diannan alone.

37:02.510 --> 37:04.440
But I didn't want to accept my fate.

37:05.910 --> 37:09.170
I didn't want to live like my parents
for the rest of my life.

37:09.420 --> 37:11.340
Until I met a fresh graduate.

37:12.940 --> 37:14.140
His name is Luo Liang.

37:16.280 --> 37:17.190
He's an orphan.

37:19.670 --> 37:20.480
His grades were bad,

37:20.480 --> 37:23.410
and he didn't want
to take the college entrance exam.

37:23.510 --> 37:24.840
I discussed it with him,

37:25.710 --> 37:26.910
bought his identity,

37:28.530 --> 37:30.030
took the exam again,

37:30.920 --> 37:32.180
and started a new life.

37:34.110 --> 37:34.960
Until today.

37:37.990 --> 37:38.850
Just like that,

37:40.230 --> 37:41.440
I went from Xiao Su

37:41.440 --> 37:42.550
to Luo Liang.

37:48.850 --> 37:49.710
Just like that?

37:54.710 --> 37:56.710
Then why didn't you tell me earlier?

38:01.510 --> 38:02.640
Maybe just like you,

38:05.510 --> 38:06.890
I didn't want to face

38:07.000 --> 38:08.530
such an embarrassing past.

38:10.990 --> 38:12.650
But I told you everything.

38:14.070 --> 38:15.360
I hid nothing from you.

38:24.630 --> 38:25.760
That time Jiale called me

38:25.760 --> 38:27.020
and said you were sick,

38:28.870 --> 38:30.330
you told me in the hospital

38:31.920 --> 38:33.720
that you got your father killed.

38:35.000 --> 38:36.460
I thought your inner demon

38:37.030 --> 38:38.890
was the guilt towards your father

38:39.920 --> 38:42.650
and the terrible relationship
with your mother.

38:43.920 --> 38:45.230
But it's not, right?

38:47.920 --> 38:49.250
You were in so much pain,

38:49.710 --> 38:50.710
so broken down.

38:53.280 --> 38:55.800
Was it because Ding Zhibo
announced the scholarship

38:55.800 --> 38:57.680
established for you on that day?

39:03.920 --> 39:06.420
But I told you about Ding Zhibo.

39:07.710 --> 39:08.710
You knew it.

39:10.360 --> 39:13.000
If he hadn't insisted on
taking that little girl away

39:13.000 --> 39:14.360
in front of you,

39:16.220 --> 39:17.820
would you still have said it?

39:26.410 --> 39:27.210
I understand.

39:30.840 --> 39:33.840
I can understand
your reservations and concealment.

39:35.320 --> 39:36.550
Because we are both

39:36.550 --> 39:38.440
fighting the pain of the past,

39:40.030 --> 39:41.560
not wanting to be defeated,

39:43.110 --> 39:43.920
while also

39:43.920 --> 39:44.880
desperately

39:45.590 --> 39:47.550
trying to hide this ugly wound.

39:50.430 --> 39:52.160
But we are all very conflicted,

39:53.480 --> 39:54.540
wanting to hide it,

39:56.320 --> 39:58.250
but also hoping that at some point,

39:59.480 --> 40:01.320
this wound could be seen

40:03.880 --> 40:04.800
and comforted.

40:11.070 --> 40:13.070
I know now is not the best time,

40:16.440 --> 40:17.370
but at least I show you

40:17.370 --> 40:18.250
mine.

40:23.320 --> 40:24.120
You know what?

40:26.400 --> 40:27.260
When you told me

40:29.400 --> 40:30.800
and confessed your past,

40:32.230 --> 40:32.710
saying

40:33.920 --> 40:34.920
not to leave you,

40:36.880 --> 40:38.190
not to leave you alone,

40:40.710 --> 40:41.800
my heart ached.

40:45.460 --> 40:46.460
For so many years,

40:48.030 --> 40:49.710
you must have cried

40:49.710 --> 40:51.240
alone on countless nights.

40:54.510 --> 40:55.650
Because I did too.

40:59.670 --> 41:00.670
I am lucky

41:02.590 --> 41:03.710
to have met you.

41:06.710 --> 41:08.670
It feels like destiny.

41:11.280 --> 41:12.070
The two of us

41:14.100 --> 41:16.630
are the best gifts
from heaven for each other.

41:20.210 --> 41:22.070
As someone who has also been hurt,

41:22.800 --> 41:25.400
I can better understand
the pain in your heart.

41:28.230 --> 41:29.360
But I also know

41:31.070 --> 41:32.600
we are different after all.

41:33.990 --> 41:35.610
I can accept all of you.

41:37.410 --> 41:38.560
But I don't expect

41:39.280 --> 41:41.080
you to make the same choice as me.

42:35.600 --> 42:37.370
[Marriage Certificate]

42:40.150 --> 42:42.040
[Marriage Certificate]

42:40.210 --> 42:42.010
If you choose to leave in the end,

42:44.840 --> 42:46.370
I can completely accept it.

42:49.230 --> 42:50.830
You can write the agreement.

42:51.880 --> 42:52.820
This house

42:53.280 --> 42:54.880
will be left to you and Jiale.

42:58.000 --> 42:59.500
Is that all you have to say?

43:04.070 --> 43:06.200
The time we had dinner with you and Mom,

43:09.940 --> 43:12.670
the woman next to me
wasn't my biological mother.

43:15.880 --> 43:18.540
I was really afraid
to let you see this side of me.

43:20.030 --> 43:21.670
So I found someone to help.

43:25.710 --> 43:27.440
I know I was ridiculous.

43:29.190 --> 43:29.920
I'm sorry.

43:44.460 --> 43:48.790
[The Dark Romance]

43:52.480 --> 43:54.700
[2000]
[Dongguang Nanshan Medical University]

44:01.000 --> 44:01.510
It's raining so heavily.

44:01.510 --> 44:02.440
Why are you here?

44:03.630 --> 44:05.760
How will you go back in such heavy rain?

44:06.920 --> 44:07.850
Then wait for me.

44:08.110 --> 44:09.110
I'll be done soon.

44:14.110 --> 44:15.120
Your hair

44:15.280 --> 44:16.540
is blocking your eyes.

44:18.850 --> 44:19.450
Stop it.

44:24.480 --> 44:26.190
Usually,
if someone asks me to cut their hair,

44:26.190 --> 44:27.450
I wouldn't be willing.

44:54.440 --> 44:55.270
Not here.

44:55.670 --> 44:57.600
We are doomed if someone finds out.

45:00.630 --> 45:01.440
It's so late.

45:04.320 --> 45:05.520
No one will come.

45:08.530 --> 45:09.590
What are you doing?

45:12.000 --> 45:12.800
Don't touch me!
